 ----------------------------------------
Norway                       15     1
United States                14     2
Austria                      13     3
Canada                       13     4
Australia                    11     5
Sweden                       11     6
New Zealand                   8     7
Finland                       6     8
France                        5     9
Denmark                       4    10
Greece                        4    11
Italy                         3    12
Germany                       3    13
Belgium and Luxembourg        2    14
Ireland                       2    15
United Kingdom                1    16
