experience refers to the risk attached to exchange delays. 4.
Individual experiences can vary considerably, depending on the
relationship with the buyer, type of goods etc. 5. All of the above
countries appear in the UK department of trade and industry's List of
Target Markets. Source: Financial Times International Trade Finance,
a bi-weekly newsletter published by Financial times Business
Enterprises.
